data.description: Multiple Offers Received!! Send Best and Final by 5pm Tuesday 2/20 Welcome Home! Your stunning oasis nestled in the center of The Balmoral Community awaits! This meticulously maintained property offers a perfect blend of modern luxury and timeless charm. Boasting 5 bedrooms and 4.5 baths, the home features a thoughtful layout with spacious living areas. The main level welcomes you with gleaming hardwood floors, setting the stage for the elegant design throughout. Step inside to discover a wealth of amenities, including a spacious game room and a cozy theater room perfect for entertaining family and friends. Pamper yourself in the convenience of your own private hair salon, designed for relaxation and indulgence. Additionally, the basement features a well-appointed bedroom and full bathroom, providing versatility and comfort for guests or extended family members. Situated in the desirable Balmoral Community, this luxurious home enjoys the benefits of community living. Get ready to enjoy the outdoors with the connecting trails that traverse the community making it both a walker and biker's paradise. This community boasts an outdoor pool and clubhouse for social gatherings as well as a gym. This home is conveniently located near shopping, dining, and major commuting routes. Do not miss the opportunity to make this extraordinary home yours. Get ready to embark on a new chapter of luxurious living!
